org.franca.core.franca

Interface FAttribute

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, FEvaluableElement, FModelElement, FTypedElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FAttributeImpl

    public interface FAttribute
extends FTypedElement
    A representation of the model object 'FAttribute'. The definition of a Franca attribute as part of an FInterface. See the Franca IDL chapter in the Franca User Guide for very detailed information on attribute semantics and the flags which can be set for attributes.

    The following features are supported:

    • Readonly
    • No Subscriptions

    See Also:
    FrancaPackage.getFAttribute()
